		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>New York</placeName> <date>24<hi rend="sup">th</hi>. Augt.</date></p>
				<p><addressee>Rev. I. Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(2)"><placeName>Pha.</placeName></p>
				<p>Rev. Dr. Sir&#33;</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">I received the proof<lb/> last <add>Hebrew</add> &#38; returned it on <date>Sunday</date>.<lb/>  I trust it reached you in time.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><sic>Inclosed</sic> the second part<lb/> of the paper on &#8220;Jewish doctrine.&#8221;<lb/>  It grows under my hand&#44; &#38; to<lb/> me appears very interesting.  If<lb/> therefore you are not tired of<lb/> it&#44; I will carry it over.  <add>&#63;</add><lb/> papers more&#8212;if not I will<lb/> squeeze it into one&#8212;Please<lb/> let me know which you prefer<lb/> &#38; oblige me with a proof.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I see&#44; you advertise a Bible<lb/> in 18 mo for &#36;2.50&#8212;with 20 <add>&#63;</add> to<lb/> those who sell&#8212;now I don&#39;t sell</p>
			<pb n="2"/>
				<p>but give away&#44; free gratis<lb/> for nothing&#8212;Assuming you<lb/> will allow me the hopes that<lb/> this is an English Bible&#8212;please<lb/> send me a copy at your<lb/> earliest convenience</p>
			<p rend="indent(7)">Yours</p>
			<p rend="indent(8)">Rev Dr Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(8)">Very Respy</p>
			<p rend="indent(8)"><persName role="author">M J Raphall</persName></p>
			
